playstore_details.title: DroidOTP
playstore_details.description:
DroidOTP is a free one-time password (OTP) client implementation.

The OTP solution provides strong authentication based on time synchronous one-time passwords and consists of a client component (this application) and a server component (available on http://motp.sourceforge.net).

DroidOTP features:
★ Supports multiple accounts based on profiles
★ Supports strict 4-digit pins a well as longer alphanumeric pins
★ Supports taking the generated password into the clipboard
★ Allows generating new password without re-entering the PIN for 50 seconds
★ Displays the current epoch time
★ Compatible with phones and tablets

Follow us on Google+: https://plus.google.com/110015161806251998661

Image: http://www.freedigitalphotos.net
